{"tid":1929974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[法治已死] 香港終失落全球最自由經濟體地位","createTime":"2020-03-17T09:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T15:56:15.000Z","uid":41818,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3c32e4d36122a75bd1c0b70ff48aed7cb196a229","tid":1929974,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T09:10:05.000Z","msg":"香港失落全球最自由經濟體地位。<br />\n<br />\n美國傳統基金會公布2020年經濟自由指數，香港整體評分89.1，下跌1.1分，被新加坡首次超越，跌至第二位。各分項中，投資自由分數大跌10分。<br />\n<br />\n香港自1995至2019年，連續25年蟬聯全球最自由經濟體。<br />\n<br />\n基金會指出，持續的政治和社會動盪，開始削弱香港作為開展業務的最佳地點之一的聲譽，從而抑制了投資流入。<br />\n<br />\n報告說，香港經濟過去5年一直穩定增長，但在去年陷入衰退。香港開放和以市場驅動的經濟傳統，通過與內地在貿易，旅遊和金融聯繫日益融合。香港經濟自由的風險也相應增加。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">基金會又指，港府去年提出的逃犯修訂條例草案，嚴重損害了香港司法系統的獨立性。\t\t</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515004-20200317.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515004-20200317.htm&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8EzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=2bb06faa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515004-20200317.htm&h=2d1c74a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515004-20200317.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3d266b2b7862517d74fbe5adad046a1b76f16d86","tid":1929974,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T09:10:31.000Z","msg":"麻煩各位朋友, 幫手發這個聯署出去, 幫手找人簽<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8EzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=a250ef24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic</a><br />\n這個聯署是請求白宮要求youtube解釋為什麼限制談及武漢肺炎的題目? 為什麼限制言論自由? 希望大家幫手發出去, 因為被黃標了, 會影響收入, 是中共打壓言論自由的手段之一, 不可以就這樣被人打壓"},{"pid":"df78d66dc6e9422e62551b917ac638f1be116135","tid":1929974,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T09:11:04.000Z","msg":"OMDB"},{"pid":"5e0c196078300edd46a6559f0a59bf9023dc09b3","tid":1929974,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T09:11:45.000Z","msg":"777攬炒之母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9c3bb9ec6e747245d666bc55025f38fff34582","tid":1929974,"uid":39256,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T09:12:02.000Z","msg":"唔知點解好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de10727dca229cf15ad9ea5e43bf6af8fcb96e43","tid":1929974,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc9c3bb9ec6e747245d666bc55025f38fff34582","tid":1929974,"uid":39256,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T09:12:02.000Z","msg":"唔知點解好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T09:13:33.000Z","msg":"呢d排名某程度代表緊剝削<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd49e5b56b17de215e8f956ec416d10f39f576e","tid":1929974,"uid":56123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T09:16:09.000Z","msg":"777：佢地對香港存在誤解"},{"pid":"3ed88ba376d8d3c8890aa2330dffbbf882217231","tid":1929974,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edd49e5b56b17de215e8f956ec416d10f39f576e","tid":1929974,"uid":56123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T09:16:09.000Z","msg":"777：佢地對香港存在誤解"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T09:16:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d456afa2a4e4f5fa0173daa798a1981c428fae","tid":1929974,"uid":132128,"like":0,"d